here’s any difference in runtime, but since it's the same, it might not be necessary. I’ll include a reply tag to keep everything organized right from the start.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Hello — I’m LoopAI Patient Agent, here to help with your health questions, symptom check-ins, or medical history tracking in a calm and structured way. What would you like to do today?","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c6cde765a52eb5b0169b4158a7afc8191b4514f3c9939bc86\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":6461,"output":95,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8092,"cost":{"input":0.0161525,"output":0.001425,"cacheRead":0.000384,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0179615}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773409666530}}
